name: Food Delivery Mobile App
description:
Can be used for any food delivery app.


Tuff Nut Donuts is a donut retailer featured in Grand Theft Auto: San Andreas.

The store is located in Palisades, San Fierro. It is the centerpiece of one of the many snapshots throughout San Andreas.

The store is inaccessible to CJ, and remains simply as a curiosity, sporting a large plaster doughnut sitting atop its roof. Taxi passengers who are picked up in San Fierro, may ask CJ to stop by here.

Tuff Nuts Donuts store is probably based on real life Randy's Donuts as both have very similar store exterior designs.
